sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_theme"><sys_ui_theme action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><css>
/* Search text color */ 
$search-text-color: #F88F33
/* Topbar background color*/
$navpage-header-bg: #28191A
/* Topbar text color */
$navpage-header-color: #E65219
/* Bottom border color on topbar */ 
$navpage-header-divider-color: #871814

/* Left nav and navigation toolbar background color */
/* Navigator hover color */
$nav-highlight-main: #0B57A3
/* Background for expanded navigation items */
$subnav-background-color: #871814
/* Backgorund for navigator (left side only). */
$navpage-nav-bg: #28191A
/* Background for Favorites list, history list, and Connect list background. */
$navpage-nav-bg-sub: #58292F
/* Text color in main navigation */
$navpage-nav-color-sub: #CED177
/* Text color when hovering over items in main nav */
$navpage-nav-mod-text-hover: #0B57A3
/* Divider color in Navigator */
$nav-hr-color: #E65219

/* Navigator tabs */
/* Active nav item underneath search and notification badge*/
$nav-highlight-bar-active: #F88F33
/* Inactive nav items underneath search */
$nav-highlight-bar-inactive: #E65219
/* Background for currently selected navigation item underneath search */
$navpage-nav-selected-bg: #F88F33
/* Color of icon for currently active nav item. */
$navpage-nav-selected-color: #28191A
/* Color of icons for non inactive nav items.*/
$navpage-nav-unselected-color: #E65219

/* Navigator Application text */
/* Color for latest connect messages in right bar. */
$connect-latest-message: #90931C
/* Timestamp header backgrounds in History tab*/
$nav-timeago-header-color: #EDD400
/* Core content text color */
$navpage-nav-app-text: #CBB260
/* Core content text color hover*/
$navpage-nav-app-text-hover: #AAD5ED                   

/* Color of outline for search */
$navpage-nav-border: #AAD5ED
/* Default button/icon colors */
$navpage-button-color:  #AAD5ED
/* Hover color for ^^^ */
$navpage-button-color-hover: #0B57A3</css><device>concourse</device><name>Star Wars: ROTS</name><sys_class_name>sys_ui_theme</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-12-26 17:24:58</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>9aa12c36db22a380ff42d540cf961920</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Star Wars: ROTS</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ui_theme_9aa12c36db22a380ff42d540cf961920</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-12-26 18:26:08</sys_updated_on></sys_ui_theme></record_update>
